{"tid":2376990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅自爆健康惡化停工！拍ＭV48小時　激動：差點哭出來","createTime":"2021-01-23T08:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T08:27:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d76ce160d27d0cb49ba014c54a012acae09a085b","tid":2376990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:21:17.000Z","msg":"南韓「性感小野馬」泫雅去（2020）年8月爆出健康惡化，不得不停工休養，新歌發行跟宣傳計畫全部延期。泫雅這陣子積極更新社群網站，預告將回歸樂壇，讓粉絲期待之餘，對泫雅的健康狀況也相當關心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/23/2997073-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F23%2F2997073-PH.jpg&h=0d830b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼泫雅將推出新專輯回歸。（圖／翻攝自泫雅IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/23/2997072-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F23%2F2997072-PH.jpg&h=cc0dd454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泫雅去年8月自爆健康惡化，她在綜藝《黃金漁場》上坦言早在10年就已經有恐慌症，過去5年間每天都需服用藥物控制，本來想說只需要隱藏一下就能正常工作，沒想到卻在拍攝廣告時暈倒，就醫後被診斷出「迷走神經性昏厥」，必須要花時間好好調養身體。泫雅直言她7歲就進入演藝圈，「過去14年間都沒休息過」，僅管每一次到醫院就診，醫生都會勸她為了健康，最好還是推掉一些工作，但她總是很難做到，也因此讓她的健康一天比一天糟糕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/23/2997071-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F23%2F2997071-PH.jpg&h=55efb255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼泫雅去年坦言被診斷出「迷走神經性昏厥」。（圖／翻攝自泫雅IG、MBC）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/27/2741775-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F27%2F2741775-PH.jpg&h=5e83d7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在休息將近半年後，泫雅在近日傳出要回歸樂壇消息，經紀公司「P Nation」預告泫雅將在28日推出新專輯《I'm Not Cool》，這也是她相隔1年2個月後回歸樂壇的作品，消息一出粉絲都相當期待。炫雅在IG上貼出MV片段，並寫下長文吐心聲，表示在準備新專輯時受到很多人幫助，雖然因求好心切而壓力很大，但能完成一件事，她感到很幸福，泫雅激動說：「在拍完48小時的MV後，真的開心到差點哭出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/23/2997075-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F23%2F2997075-PH.jpg&h=e536c1d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼泫雅PO出MV片段。（圖／翻攝自泫雅IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/01/23/2997074-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F01%2F23%2F2997074-PH.jpg&h=24b81e17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c4436196b046ea97cc150d91868d70c93453f08","tid":2376990,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:25:46.000Z","msg":"吸毒吸得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d748b18623448d5a1dffab6f949755356be559a3","tid":2376990,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"咸左😭"}]}